<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٢٩ ... سُورَةُ العَنْكَبُوتِ ... آياتها ٦٩ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يُفْتَنُونَ}</span> ... لَا يُخْتَبَرُونَ بِالشَّدَائِدِ؛ لِيَتَبَيَّنَ المُؤْمِنُ مِنَ المُنَافِقِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْبِقُونَا}</span> ... يُعْجِزُونَا، وَيَفُوتُونَا بِأَنْفُسِهِمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَجَلَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... الوَقْتَ الَّذِي حَدَّدَهُ اللهُ لِلْبَعْثِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِتْنَةَ النَّاسِ}</span> ... عَذَابَ النَّاسِ لَهُ، وَأَذَاهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلَنَا}</span> ... دِينَنَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثْقَالَهُمْ}</span> ... أَوْزَارَهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَفْتَرُونَ}</span> ... يَخْتَلِقُونَ مِنَ الكَذِبِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَخْلُقُونَ إِفْكًا}</span> ... تَفْتَرُونَ كَذِبًا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَابْتَغُوا}</span> ... الْتَمِسُوا وَاطْلُبُوا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَدَأَ الْخَلْقَ}</span> ... أَنْشَأَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُقْلَبُونَ}</span> ... تُرَدُّونَ، وَتُرْجَعُونَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمُعْجِزِينَ}</span> ... فَائِتِينَ مِنْ عَذَابِهِ بِالهَرَبِ وَغَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّوَدَّةَ بَيْنِكُمْ}</span> ... تَتَحَابُّونَ عَلَى عِبَادَتِها، وتَتَوَادُّونَ عَلَى خِدْمَتِهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَكْفُرُ}</span> ... يَتَبَرَّأُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَاوَاكُمُ}</span> ... مَصِيرُكُمْ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُهَاجِرٌ}</span> ... تَارِكٌ دَارَ قَوْمِي إِلَى أَرْضِ الشَّامِ المُبَارَكَةِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>